Introduction
------------

	This library was writed to provide a flexible layout engine
	for your hardware interfaces. It uses the standard Amiga resources
    to do this.


Hardware ports supported
------------------------

	Parallel 		(Full Tested)
	Joy		 		(Partial Tested)
	Serial	 		(Not yet functionally)
	Drive	 		(Not yet implemented)
	Audio Filter	(Tested)

Developers
----------

	This is a beta release, so i've not provided examples of the use 
	of this library.
	For the complete list of the functions you can refer to:

	doc/io.doc
	guide/io.guide
	fd/io.fd
	libraries/io.h


